						<div class="services__icon rotate-8__icon max-w-[100px] w-[100%] flex-shrink-0 grid place-items-center">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><!--!Font Awesome Free 6.5.2 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2024 Fonticons, Inc.-->
